contentrichtext.text: '''Plantation''' is the name of the following places in the U.S. state of Florida: *[[Plantation, Florida]], a city in Broward County; the largest of the places named "Plantation" in Florida *[[Plantation, Sarasota County, Florida]], a census-designated place *[[Plantation Island, Florida]], a census-designated place in Collier County *[[Plantation Key]], an island in Monroe County and part of the Florida Keys **[[Plantation Key, Florida]], a former census-designated place in Monroe County {{geodis}}
